column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.petroMag_r,p.extinction_r,p.petroR5#_r,ISNULL(s.z,#) as redshift,s.velDisp,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   (p.petroR9#_r/p.petroR5#_r) > #  AND (p.petroMag_g - p.petroMag_r) > #  AND p.petroMag_r > # AND p.petroMag_r < #  AND p.petroMagErr_r < #  AND s.z < #  AND s.zErr < #e-#  AND s.velDisp > #  AND (s.velDispErr/s.velDisp) < #
